column12: Leaf Dry Matter Content (LDMC; dry mass / fresh mass)
column23: Root Dry Matter Content (RDMC: dry mass / fresh mass)
column24: Specific Root Area (SRA: root surface area / dry mass) (mm2.g-1)
column26: Specific Root Length (SRL: root length/root dry weight) (cm.g-1)
column33: fine:coarse root ratio (volume of fine root (<0.5mm diametre) / volume of coarse root (>0.5mm diametre))
column41: Life form (1 = phanerophytes; 2 = chamaephytes; 3 = hemicryptophytes; 4 = geophytes; 5 = therophytes)
column46: B (root biomass depth distribution coefficient (Gale and Grigal 1987))
